de.erichseifert.gral.data.filters

Class Kernel

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.erichseifert.gral.data.filters.Kernel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Kernel
extends Object
implements Serializable

    Class that represents an one dimensional array of coefficients for a weighted filtering.

    Functionality includes:

    • Adding of other kernels or scalars
    • Multiplication with other kernels or scalars
    • Normalization
    • Negation
    See Also:
